      <title>交易员在美国大选波动前抛售新兴债券 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/traders-sell-emerging-bond-etfs-ahead-of-us-election-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员在周二至关重要的美国大选前降低风险，投资者在 10 月份从购买新兴市场债券的交易所交易基金 (ETF) 中撤出资金，而大选结果仍需掷硬币决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/traders-sell-emerging-bond-etfs-ahead-of-us-election-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:17:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
